description:
Judas Iscariot tells of his early ministry with Jesus. He also describes dinner at the house of a Pharisee, the healing of the man with swelling, and counting the cost of being a disciple of Jesus. The basis for this episode is Luke 14. From the Luke Series Scripture References: Luke 14: 1-33
